  "shortDescription": "An elf warlock who traded his soul to a fiend for the power to break his people's chains.",
  "description": "Caelen Vyr watched the White Capes brand his kin as unsanctioned and herd them off the rolls, and he decided the only law that mattered was the one with teeth. In a ruin the Capes had forgotten, he cut a bargain with a thing from the Lower Planes — power now, and the long account settled later. Eldritch fire answers his hand. Vengeance answers his patience."
